$5 P&P TO EVERYWHERE

*WAS $35, NOW $30*

Our Social Conscience:
We work with ‘Print Side Up’ – a drop-in employment, education and training support service for young people, based at Melbourne City Mission’s Youth Enterprise Hub. Through PSU, young people develop important employability skills, manual screen-print techniques and are provided with an outlet for their creative expression. This opens their minds and captures their interest, while increasing their chances of future employment. Find out more at printsideup.org.au.
